{"tid":1927812,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"馬會 可以考慮以下投注項目","createTime":"2020-03-16T04:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T05:35:00.000Z","uid":2207,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ef11d606540ef02153625b9f6e59daac83cd6efd","tid":1927812,"uid":2207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:23:26.000Z","msg":"而家無哂英超, 西甲, 德甲, 意甲<br />\n馬會投注額一定少左好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以考慮用平時足球模式黎出呢啲項目<br />\n<br />\n1. 下隊入球 -&gt; 下個爆發國家<br />\n2. 入球大細 -&gt; 確診人數<br />\n3. 意大利 vs 中國 -&gt; 主客和 -&gt; 邊隊最後確診人數最多<br />\n4. 「肺炎」會發生在「各國總統」身上?<br />\na. Trump b. 林鄭 c. 維尼 d. 金仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有得買, 我買澳洲下隊入球 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83fe452d4bfb12a1291d0e9d577d7766a46636e","tid":1927812,"uid":64131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:27:26.000Z","msg":"意大利初盤讓一球中水 (一百萬人)<br />\n後市持續資金湧入<br />\n尾盤外圍轉哂一球/球半<br />\n馬會企硬一球盤低水<br />\n預料輕鬆穿盤<br />\n可直屌主其他"},{"pid":"db321848d729c8615b799240b7c36558948401f9","tid":1927812,"uid":2207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a83fe452d4bfb12a1291d0e9d577d7766a46636e","tid":1927812,"uid":64131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:27:26.000Z","msg":"意大利初盤讓一球中水 (一百萬人)<br />\n後市持續資金湧入<br />\n尾盤外圍轉哂一球/球半<br />\n馬會企硬一球盤低水<br />\n預料輕鬆穿盤<br />\n可直屌主其他"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:35:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n讓一球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"